Name: Fallout 4 Workshop Extended
Author: CrowsBane
Description: F4WE is a Sim Settlements 2 focused modlist staying close to vanilla with some Quality of Life seasoning.

State.Name: FallOpt - Lightweight ENB for Vanilla weather
State.Author: SpringHeelJon
State.Description: Featured in the Welcome to Paradise Wabbajack modlist by Phoenix, FallOpt is an optimized ENB for the vanilla weather system.

State.Name: xSE PluginPreloader F4
State.Author: Karandra
State.Description: This mod allows preload F4SE plugins before the game initializes.

State.Name: Buffout 4
State.Author: Ryan
State.Description: It's like buffout but for the engine

State.Name: Automatron Load Screen Fix
State.Author: stoker25
State.Description: Changes the chance of Automatron loading screens from 20% to 1%

State.Name: Better Companions - No Conflicts
State.Author: Recluse
State.Description: Combines the effects of Companion Infinite Ammo, No Companion Power Armor Damage, Companions Can Sneak, and No Companion Fall Damage, for vanilla, DLC, and Mod Companions, WITHOUT making any edits to vanilla records and WITHOUT scripts. No overwrites, no conflicts. Now with Increased Companion Accuracy option.

State.Name: BS Defence - This Settlement Does Not Need Your Help
State.Author: Rcoll
State.Description: Better Settlement Defence - Makes those hundreds of turrets actually do something when you're not around by taking away the random aspect of settlement attacks.

State.Name: Canary Save File Monitor
State.Author: kinggath
State.Description: Monitors your save file for data loss and warns you when you load the game, so you can avoid wasting time playing on a busted save and roll back immediately.

State.Name: Choochoo1's Workshop Framework displays
State.Author: Choochoo1
State.Description: This mod adds several displays for your items as well as a few random clutter items for your settlments. Allowing you show off your favorite weapon, store all that Nuka Cola you have been carrying around  or place your magazines on a more space efficient wall shelf.

State.Name: Clarity - A Visual Overhaul
State.Author: Bretton
State.Description: A zero performance loss, very subtle visual overhaul. Removes many annoying visuals in the game.

State.Name: Commonwealth Climate - A Vanilla Plus Weather Mod
State.Author: Qolore7
State.Description: Makes Fallout 4 a little more bleak/post-apocalyptic without completely changing the game's aesthetics

Archives.Name: Follower Stealth Distance Fix (No Free Hugs) - ESL-tagged-15823-7-0-1620077127.7z

State.Name: Companion Stealth Distance Fix (No Free Hugs) - Now with No Dogmeat in Crosshairs
State.Author: spacefiddle
State.Description: A simple change that prevents your companion from charging up your posterior at full speed whenever you enter stealth. Also slightly increases their follow distance. Now also prevents Dogmeat from entering player crosshairs every damn time you stop!

State.Name: Configurable Hotkeys
State.Author: Dank Rafft
State.Description: Configure several hotkeys via MCM that allow you to create standard saves, use items, wait anywhere, execute console commands or custom functions.

State.Name: Creation Club - Better Military Backpack Distribution
State.Author: Hackfield
State.Description: A backpack won't magically appear in your inventory when installing the mod, instead, a blue Vault-Tec backpack is placed in Vault 111. Also, world distributed backpacks will now have random colors and modifications.

State.Name: cVc Dead Wasteland
State.Author: cVc
State.Description: This workshop add-on pack adds 1000s of unique, lore friendly items to build in your settlements. Script injected, adding a new menu 'cVc'

State.Name: cVc Dead Wasteland
State.Author: cVc

State.Name: FallUI - Map
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description: Overhaul of the Fallout 4 map. Added list of locations and workshops including text search. Add favorite locations to fast travel with one click. Many Quality-Of-Life features like disabling the popup on empty map space click, better map zoom steps, travel and arrival time. Colored marker support. Including high-res map texture support.

State.Name: FallUI - Sleep and Wait
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description:
Overhaul of the sleeping and waiting menu for Fallout 4. 

Directly click on your desired wake-up time with target time buttons. See the daylight level at target time in the daytime graph and more. Interface available in all languages.

State.Name: FallUI - Workbench
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description: Better workbench interface optimized for PC. Bigger display size. Data columns. Comparision columns for mods. Item icon tag support. Icon menu for choosing your icon tag. Item subtitles. Autobuilding modules with zero cost. All languages included.

State.Name: FAR - Faraway Area Reform
State.Author: SparrowPrince
State.Description: FAR optimises and improves over six thousand distant land textures, which means more perfomance and less stutter.

State.Name: Fixed Alpha Maps
State.Author: ScottyX2 and Neolithicjay
State.Description: Fixes Bethesda's shoddy, non-existent alpha maps.

State.Name: Fixed Creature Death Drops
State.Author: Lively
State.Description: Fixes LLD (Leveled List Death) records. Creatures don't drop junk and caps on death. Dogs and Mutant hounds can drop blood samples for the Brotherhood.

State.Name: Fixed Gobo Effects
State.Author: Ablaze666
State.Description: This mod fixes artefacts, pixelation and color banding in textures that are used for special light effects. Zero performance loss, little to nothing strain for your VRAM, no esp needed, no reason to not use it.

State.Name: Flicker Fixer
State.Author: Glass
State.Description: Fixes most of the exterior flickering aka z fighting in the game, particularly in the Boston and Cambridge areas.

Archives.Name: Fortune Finder 4 Fix - Basic Bottlecap Mine-43740-1-1-1583316002.7z

State.Name: Fortune Finder 4 Fix
State.Author: Whisper
State.Description:
An intense firefight, several opponents have exploded into caps. Money! Yay! Now that you're done, night's coming on and you've got to find the piles of caps spread all over...in the coming darkness...



...yeah screw that. Put those caps in my pocket, since you're that immersive and all. Same for them there Bottlecap Mines.

State.Name: Gear Grinder
State.Author: IDontEvenKnow
State.Description: Think stripping things down for parts is as tedious as I do? Here's a machine to automate the process.

State.Name: Graf's Security Fences
State.Author: GrafPanzer
State.Description: Adds buildable, snappable barbed-wire topped security fences to the Workshop Fences menu.  Variants have sheet metal screening or concrete block reinforcement.  Script-added menu plays nicely with other mods.  Now with pre-war variants and auto-closing gates.  Versión en español disponible.

State.Name: HUDFramework
State.Author: registrator2000
State.Description: HUDFramework is a UI framework that makes it possible for mods to add new UI elements to the HUD.

State.Name: IDEK's Logistics Station 2
State.Author: IDontEvenKnow
State.Description:
Now with support for SimSettlements 1 and 2, or no SS at all!

Adds a system to automatically manage supply lines, improve the efficiency of inter-settlement resource sharing, and adds a handful of minor convenience features.

State.Name: Immersive HUD - iHUD
State.Author: Gopher
State.Description: HUD when you need. Hide when you don't.

State.Name: Jamaica Plain Navmesh Fix
State.Author: HoodieGyaru
State.Description: Fixes the navigation mesh in Jamaica Plain to allow NPCs to use the stairs in front of the Workshop building. An alternate version is also included that allows NPCs to path in the middle of Jamaica Plain instead of around it.

State.Name: Laser weapons 1st person reposition
State.Author: akir4 and Wardaddy
State.Description: Makes the institute and standard laser weapons smaller in the 1st person.

State.Name: Less Ugly Intercom
State.Author: Ablaze666
State.Description: This small mod replaces the square-ish light effect on intercoms with a round one.

State.Name: MCM Settings Manager
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description: Save, load, transfer, import and export all your MCM settings at once. Transfer settings between savegames, backup your favorite settings, or send your settings to another user!

State.Author: IceKK
State.Description: Disabled Mouse Acceleration, Horizontal/Vertical Parity, Scalable ADS Multiplier, Normalized Sensitivity

State.Name: Raze My Settlement
State.Author: Whisper
State.Description:
Are you sick of scrapping your settlements to the ground so you can build on them? Me too.



One click of a button in a holotape - gone in sixty seconds! (Depending upon the power of your gaming rig.)

Archives.Name: Rise of the Commonwealth for SS2-50684-1-0-10-1616168727.7z

State.Name: Rise of the Commonwealth for Sim Settlements 2
State.Author: Sim Settlements Team
State.Description: Collection of 36 upgradeable City Plans for Sim Settlements 2, covering every vanilla and DLC settlement!

State.Name: Ruddy88's Simple Sorter
State.Author: Ruddy88
State.Description: Simple Sorter is a FO4Edit script that will automatically add the text needed for icon replacements for all valid items in your entire load order. It automatically scans your mod list, loads all valid items to a new ESP, then detects what sort of item it is so that the correct icons are used. No more patches, no more manually patching.

State.Name: Rusty Face Fix
State.Author: Seb263
State.Description: This mod fixes this annoying bug that makes the player's and NPCs faces turn brown when reloading a savegame. It is completely transparent, autonomous, has no impact on performance and is compatible with any mods.

State.Name: Sandbox Radius Overhaul 2x
State.Author: Hamper
State.Description: This mod overhauls pretty much every package there is to be twice the original distance. Settlers, citizens, companions, townsfolk, traders, everybody will wander twice as far around for improved immersion.

State.Name: Screen Flicker Killer and no blur effect
State.Author: Fl0W
State.Description: Removes the flickering from the PipBoy and Computer screens. And also changes the overbright glowing effect from the PipBoy (especial on the PowerArmor screen)

State.Name: Settlement Menu Manager
State.Author: cadpnq
State.Description: SMM provides an easy way to add custom menus and makes said menus automatically disappear on uninstall (without breaking your build menu!)

State.Name: Sim Settlements 2
State.Author: Sim Settlements Team
State.Description: Sequel to the Fallout 4 city-building simulator.

State.Name: Sim Settlements 2 - Chapter 2
State.Author: Sim Settlements Team
State.Description:
Fight off settler disease, repopulate the world outside of your settlements, battle the Gunners, and establish your own faction headquarters to rule the Commonwealth!



Chapter 2 continues the story of SS2, adds in 3 new side questlines, and adds tons of new features to enjoy outside of the story content.

State.Name: Sim Settlements 2 Automatron Mod
State.Author: pra
State.Description: Makes automatron modifications affect their SPECIAL stats for Sim Settlements 2 plots.

State.Name: Sim Settlements 2 Wasteland Reconstruction Kit
State.Author: Sim Settlements Team
State.Description: Over 10,000 buildable items provided through Sim Settlements 2, including dozens of prefab building models!

State.Name: Snappable Junk Fences
State.Author: DarthWayne
State.Description: This mod solves the old problem of useless fences with large gaps between them by adding snap points to the junk fences and guard towers. This enables you to snap them gapless together. Furthermore you can snap floors as walkways to some of the fences.

State.Name: Sim Settlements 2
State.Author: Sim Settlements Team
State.Description: Sequel to the Fallout 4 city-building simulator.

State.Name: Starlight Drive In LOD Fix with ESL
State.Author: neeher
State.Description: Was always annoyed with how the Drive In would fade into view when walking up to it. Can now be seen properly from far away. More immersive. ESL Version Available.

State.Name: Take Your Cores
State.Author: darkconsole
State.Description: Automatically yank Fusion Cores out of power armor when you get out.

Archives.Name: There It Is x Perfectionist x No PA-50927-1-0-1616364827.7z

State.Name: There It Is - Satellite Maps For Collectors
State.Author: SaiSei
State.Description: Comprehensive collectors edition of the satellite world maps.

State.Name: Unofficial Fallout 4 Patch
State.Author: Unofficial Patch Project Team
State.Description: A comprehensive bugfixing mod for Fallout 4. The goal of the Unofficial Fallout 4 Patch (aka UFO4P) is to eventually fix every bug with Fallout 4 not officially resolved by the developers to the limits of the Creation Kit and community-developed tools, in one easy-to-install package.

State.Name: Vault 88 Essentials
State.Author: SethNorris
State.Description: Combination, improvement and bug fixing for several popular Vault 88 Kit mods plus a small set of additions. The bare essentials for a proper Vault building experience.

State.Name: Vault 88 Template - Optimised
State.Author: RyReZar
State.Description: This mod adds Room Bounds and Portals to a custom template of Vault 88 which gives greater optimisation and allows a bigger vault to be built, essentially increasing the build limit.

State.Name: Vault-Tec Tools - Sim Settlements 2 Addon Pack
State.Author: Samutz and Wulfharth
State.Description: A Sim Settlements 2 Addon Pack containing 22 vault-themed interior plot plans, 2 city planner desks, 4 flags, and several vault-specific features.

State.Name: Vault-Tec Workshop Overhaul Redux (VTWOR)
State.Author: litbeep
State.Description: A non-intrusive mod that aims to fix inconsistencies within the Vault-Tec Workshop DLC. This version addresses lighting and texture issues, adds light snapping to walls and ceilings, adds sign snapping to doors, enables crate stacking, and makes some minor quality-of-life changes.

State.Name: Visible Idle Markers
State.Author: Whisper
State.Description: So you built something in your settlement - only to find that your settlers "phase in" to it, because there's an idle marker there. No more - now you can see the base game idle markers while in workshop mode.

State.Name: WAVE - Wave Animation Vanilla Enhanced
State.Author: SparrowPrince
State.Description: No more elastic waves in the Commonwealth. Brand new effects and textures with a more realistic motion.

State.Name: Weapon Wall Racks (WWR)
State.Author: jkruse05
State.Description: Modular storage racks to attach to walls.

State.Name: Weston Water LOD Fix
State.Author: ossumpossum
State.Description: Flags water at the Weston Water Treatment Plant with IsFullLOD so it is visible and no longer pops in.

State.Name: WET - Water Enhancement Textures
State.Author: SparrowPrince
State.Description: WET enhances all water and most water-related effects in the game. From one of the creators of the popular Realistic Water Two mod for Skyrim.

State.Name: Wetness Shader Fix
State.Author: Ablaze666
State.Description: This small mod fixes the exaggerated shine of specific objects while it's raining.

State.Name: Whisper's Extra Pieces and Snaps
State.Author: Whisper and Karvoc and Others
State.Description: Some extra kitbashed floors and ceilings, and extra snap-points upon many vanilla wood/metal build-items.

State.Name: Workshop Framework
State.Author: kinggath
State.Description:
Framework to open up the settlement system to editing by the community.



For Players: New controls and faster, more stable workshop scripts.



For Modders: Add new resource types, override settings, and generally change the way settlements work dynamically.

State.Name: Workshop Plus
State.Author: kinggath
State.Description:
Transforms Workshop mode into a God simulator - giving you all of the tools you need to create amazing settlements. 



Flight, Undo Buttons, Layers, Cloning Tools, Free Build Mode, and more!

State.Name: Bullet Counted Reload System (BCR)
State.Author: shavkacagarikia
State.Description: Finally, a proper engine-level system for bullet counted reloads with most of the features such a system should have.

State.Name: Better Console - F4SE
State.Author: Kassent
State.Description: This is a F4SE plugin which makes console menu show extra useful infomation about selected target,for example, target's name, ID, baseID, mod name and so on.This plugin also add some extra info lists to console to show selected actor's all kinds of info like factions, perks, active effects, actor values, equipments and so on.

State.Name: Bullet Counted Reload System (BCR)
State.Author: shavkacagarikia
State.Description: Finally, a proper engine-level system for bullet counted reloads with most of the features such a system should have.

State.Name: CCCleaner
State.Author: Neanka
State.Description: clean all about CC from ur game interface

State.Name: Clock Widget - Show Real Time While Loading
State.Author: Kassent
State.Description: This mod adds a clock widget to loading menu, main menu and fader menu to display current real time while loading.How much time did you spend on loading?

Archives.Name: DEF_UI Iconlibs Rescaled and Fixed - Colored-31088-1-6-1575705975.7z

State.Name: DEF_UI Iconlibs Rescaled and Fixed
State.Author: Phlunder
State.Description: Aims to bring consistency in design and coloring to the icon library. Also fixes various issues with icon sizes, bounding boxes, and scaling.

State.Name: FallUI - Inventory
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description: This is FallUI - Inventory. A optimized Fallout 4 inventory interface for PC.

State.Name: FallUI - Confirm Boxes (incl. Yes Im Sure)
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description: Overhaul of all confirm box interfaces. Including different designs and styles for many box types (configurable). You can also choose to disable confirms, so it automatically accept without confirmation (like "Yes Im Sure"). Interface covers all languages.

State.Name: FallUI - HUD
State.Author: m8r98a4f2
State.Description: A highly configurable HUD. Every widget can be positioned and configured. Configure your design in the in-game layout manager in MCM. Layouts can be shared and imported too.

Archives.Name: Full Dialogue Interface - All languages - NMM installer - Beta12-1235-Beta12.zip

State.Name: Full Dialogue Interface (NewDialog English and CN-DE-ES-FR-IT-JA-PL-PTBR-RU translations)
State.Author: Cirosan and shadwar
State.Description: Makes the game display the full lines of what your character is going to say in conversation, instead of just a paraphrase. It also revamps the interface so that the game will now display dialogue options in a list and use the number keys/face buttons for input, depending on your control scheme. Supports both keyboard and gamepad.

State.Name: Mod Configuration Menu
State.Author: reg2k - Neanka - shadowslasher410
State.Description: The Mod Configuration Menu is a settings page for mods! It provides a central location for mod configuration, accessible via the Pause menu.

State.Name: Place Everywhere
State.Author: TheLich
State.Description: Place/build objects in settlements everywhere you want, change objects whatever you like. No more RED!

State.Name: Address Library for F4SE Plugins
State.Author: Ryan
State.Description: Provides version independent IDs used for dynamically relocating offsets at runtime.

State.Name: Buffout 4
State.Author: Ryan
State.Description: It's like buffout but for the engine

State.Name: Classic Holstered Weapons System (CHW)

State.Name: Encounter Zone Recalculation (Continuous Level Scaling)

State.Author: boring3

Make Fallout 4 always take most of CPU usage

Increase FPS and Prevent suddenly lag caused by other processes

State.Name: Faster Workshop (Workshop Lag Fix)
State.Author: reg2k
State.Description: Faster Workshop is an F4SE plugin that optimizes workshop loading times by replacing some of the most expensive and inefficient regions of workshop loading code with far more efficient versions. Also provides a hotkey to instantly enter Workshop mode and fixes workshop icon load lag.

State.Name: High FPS Physics Fix
State.Author: Antonix35
State.Description:
Untie the game speed from the framerate. Fixes physical bugs. Reduces loading time.

Now there is a separate version for VR.

State.Name: Power Armor HoloHUD
State.Author: mluppov
State.Description: This will replace ridiculous half transparent... whatever it is with something much nicer.

State.Name: Power Armor map fix
State.Author: Spanian77
State.Description: Changes the texture material used for not having over-brighten map when using power armor.

State.Name: R2K's Gameplay Mods
State.Author: registrator2000
State.Description: A collection of mods and ends.

State.Name: Sprint Stuttering Fix
State.Author: AntoniX
State.Description:
Fixed twitching/stuttering when sprinting in first person.



Исправление дрожания камеры от первого лица при спринте.

Fixed crashes caused by Weapon Debris setting



Исправление вылетов при включенной настройке "Осколки от выстрелов"

State.Name: Whose Quest Is It Anyway
State.Author: Ryan
State.Description: Swap the "quest items can't be removed" message with something a little more informative.

State.Name: Clean Black Pip-Boy Screen
State.Author: GodMod99 Bryce
State.Description: As simple as it is beautiful, makes the pip-boy screen perfectly black. Tired of that weird greenish brown background for your blue, white, red or any colour of text? Well this is just what you need!

State.Name: Decayed Army Fatigues Fix
State.Author: radbeetle
State.Description: the transparency was really bad on these so i made it less bad

State.Name: Glowing Glass Fix
State.Author: Kouta554
State.Description:
A really small fix for the glowing glass window that bothered me since i started playing this game. 

For now i just edited one file, so maybe there is still more to fix.

If i find more, i'll try to work on it and fix it.

State.Name: Institute Floor Fix
State.Author: SpringHeelJon
